# ── CafePos web — environment variables ───────────────────────────────────────
# Copy to .env.local for local overrides. In production (Vercel) set these in
# Project → Settings → Environment Variables, then redeploy.

# Base URL of the deployed CafePos API. REQUIRED in production.
#   - Local dev: leave UNSET — the Vite proxy forwards /api to http://localhost:5088.
#   - Vercel:    set to your deployed backend, e.g. https://cafepos-api.onrender.com
# The frontend then calls the API directly (the backend must allow this site's origin
# via CORS — set CAFEPOS_CORS_ORIGINS on the backend to your Vercel URL).
VITE_API_URL=
